{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"AgentSight","page":{"layout":"document","title":"AgentSight Website","description":"Static product website for agentsight.us.","descriptionIsExcerpt":true,"bodyHtml":"<p>Static product website for <code>agentsight.us</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"quick-start\">Quick Start</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">npm</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> install</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">npm</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> dev</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"build\">Build</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">npm</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> build</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>The static export is written to <code>out/</code> and is intended for Cloudflare Pages.</p>","headings":[{"id":"quick-start","text":"Quick Start","depth":2},{"id":"build","text":"Build","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/agentsight/website/README.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2026-06-24T06:41:13.000Z","createdAt":"2026-06-24T06:41:13.000Z","authors":[{"name":"github-actions[bot]","email":"41898282+github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com"}]},"path":"/zh/agentsight/website/","alternates":{"en":"/agentsight/website/","zh":"/zh/agentsight/website/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"AgentSight：基于 eBPF 的零侵入 LLM 智能体可观测性工具","description":"![License: MIT](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT) ![CI](https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/agentsight/actions/workflows/ci.yml)","href":"/zh/agentsight/"},"previous":{"title":"User Instructions","description":"不需要看 claude 了, 你去开一个新的 worktree, 把这些都实现一下, 然后给我看图, 1. 像素/行级系 —— SeeSoft(Eick,贝尔实验室,1992) 一切的祖师爷。每行代码压缩成一个像素行,颜色编码年龄/作者/修改次数,一屏塞下几万行。\"代码年龄热图\"这个概念就是它发明的。它的直系后代活得最好:GitLens 在编辑器里的 blame 热图、git blame 的各种可视化,本质都是","href":"/zh/agentsight/user-instruction/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"AgentSight","items":[{"title":"总览","href":"/zh/agentsight/"},{"title":"快速开始","href":"/zh/agentsight/usage/"},{"title":"支持的智能体","href":"/zh/agentsight/agents/"},{"title":"从源码构建","href":"/zh/agentsight/build/"},{"title":"Docker 部署","href":"/zh/agentsight/docker/"},{"title":"OpenTelemetry 集成","href":"/zh/agentsight/otel/"},{"title":"agentpprof","href":"/zh/agentsight/agentpprof/"},{"title":"开发指南","href":"/zh/agentsight/development/"}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}